entries.UNIT_EVO_SELECT: Select a Unit (1-Star to 7-Star) for Evolution or an Omni Unit for Omni+ Boost. Units that are dimmed cannot be Evolved or Boosted.
entries.UNIT_NOT_PERMIT_APPEND_MAX_OMNI_BOOST: ・A fully boosted Unit for boosting has been included
entries.UNIT_NOT_PERMIT_APPEND_NOT_SAME_ID: ・A different Unit for boosting has been included
entries.UNIT_NOT_PERMIT_APPEND_OMNI_BOOST_BASE: ・A base Unit for boosting has been included
entries.UNIT_OMNI_EVO_DUP_SELECTION_TICKER: Select a Duplicate Unit. Units that are dimmed cannot be used as Ingredients.
entries.UNIT_OMNI_EVO_ONE_TIME_WARNING_MSG:
If you use this Unit as an Ingredient,
it may become unavailable in the future.
Proceed?
entries.UNIT_OMNI_EVO_TICKER: The Boost button is only active when you have the required Omni+ Boost Materials, Zel & Karma.
entries.UNIT_OMNI_EVO_USE_BOOSTED_MSG: A boosted Unit (+1 or higher) has been selected as Ingredient. Are you sure you want to proceed?
